# StrategyVault app — environment

# --- fork test (optional) ---
# The fork test defaults to a public RPC and needs no key. Override for a reliable archive node:
MAINNET_RPC_URL=https://ethereum-rpc.publicnode.com

# --- real-money script (script/RealSwap.s.sol) — DO NOT fill unless you mean it ---
# Foundry auto-loads a .env from this directory. To run the gated real swap, copy this file to
# .env here and set a VALID 0x-prefixed 32-byte key (the repo-root placeholder is intentionally
# corrupted so it cannot run by accident). Fund the address with USDC + ETH for gas first.
REAL_MONEY_PKEY=0x<your_real_key_here>
# AMOUNT_IN=5000000   # optional, USDC 6dp (default 5 USDC)

# --- CRE workflow (added in the next milestone) ---
# CRE_ETH_PRIVATE_KEY=<raw 64-char hex, no 0x>   # only for --broadcast
# CRE_TARGET=staging-settings
